This was really good. I did follow the advice of straining the orange peel. Just for info, I would bring cream, milk, and orange peel to simmer BEFORE mixing the egg yolks with the sugar. If you mix those two too soon, the sugar can "cook" the eggs and it just won't turn out the same.

